# Xcode
#
# gitignore contributors: remember to update Global/Xcode.gitignore, Objective-C.gitignore & Swift.gitignore

## User settings
xcuserdata/

## Scripts
*.python-version

## Build results
DerivedData/
build/
Build/
Index/
Logs/

## Dependencies
### Carthage
Carthage/Build/
### CocoaPods
# We recommend against committing the Pods directory to your repository.
# However, if you'd like to commit your Pods directory, remove the Pods/ line.
Pods/
# If you are using versioning for your pods, you might want to ignore the Podfile.lock as well
# Podfile.lock
### Swift Package Manager
# Ignore the Swift Package Manager build directory
.build/
# Ignore the Swift Package Manager resolved file, it's recommended to commit this file
# Package.resolved

## Testing
*.moved-aside
*.xcuserstate
*.xcresult

## macOS
# General
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride

# Icon must end with two \r
Icon


# Thumbnails
._*

